{"tid":629371,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[理性討論]點先算爛尾","createTime":"2018-04-14T15:37:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T06:48:57.000Z","uid":119012,"like":0,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"98586d32c6ec904194dd87f46cb2395bf43ad849","tid":629371,"uid":119012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T15:37:40.000Z","msg":"想知大家對爛尾嘅定義係點?<br />\n就拎長年都比人評為爛尾嘅偽戀同火影黎講<br />\n其實呢2套真係爛尾咩?<br />\n雖然我係小野寺派 但故事發展令人渣樂同千棘一齊相當合理喎 背景又係現代日本 無理由開後宮 開放式故事肯定比人插到飛起 雖然係急左少少 但個尾其實收得幾靚<br />\n跟住係火影 唔講動畫 唔講博人傳<br />\n無一堆回憶殺的話其實故事流程相當流暢每一個人物塑造得勁鮮明 都比佢一個結局 係最尾輝夜出現有啲莫名奇妙 但個ending其實幾好 <br />\n如果話真正爛尾爛到痴線我覺得係Charlotte囉"},{"pid":"3c0e48fd05785478cd6b81bdd2b9baddf3221fdd","tid":629371,"uid":34609,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T15:39:42.000Z","msg":"A/Z 笑而不語 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f98de2564726a380a682be555d3a384d7cd529a5","tid":629371,"uid":49057,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T15:43:31.000Z","msg":"Charlotte唔係爛尾，奈緒最後嗰集個笑容真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89cb55cf4cc2161a532ef05b2bd9dc94c3dc9e43","tid":629371,"uid":82404,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T15:47:35.000Z","msg":"偽戀唔算爛尾啦<br />\n係由中段開始爛到落尾<br />\n火影個尾我就不嬲都覺得好睇"},{"pid":"4243f90b064b84c3ed515374378464cc1f63984a","tid":629371,"uid":13151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T16:02:47.000Z","msg":"魔法戰爭"},{"pid":"84b0c69d412d1269f391380ea45946878afe4814","tid":629371,"uid":61443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T16:03:58.000Z","msg":"有啲趕埋尾返屋企食飯衝收工果啲"},{"pid":"d1c9f376749bcf1a402aff8b830e158a67da73fe","tid":629371,"uid":73627,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"89cb55cf4cc2161a532ef05b2bd9dc94c3dc9e43","tid":629371,"uid":82404,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T15:47:35.000Z","msg":"偽戀唔算爛尾啦<br />\n係由中段開